Requirements: 
Docker installed
Git installed
Node 20.15

# STEP 1 - Clone the repository and submodules
git clone --recurse-submodules <repoURL>

# In case you cloned the repo without the recurse flag, run these Init and update submodules commands
git submodule init
git submodule update

# Run project
To use application go to repository folder (gilaNotificationsNest) and run in terminal:
  `docker-compose build`
  `docker-compose up -d`

# Access app
Frontend app: http://localhost:3000
API URL: http://localhost:3001

# Database access
Connect to database from localhost:
  Host: localhost
  User: root
  Password: admin
  Port: 3307
